subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: George Zahringer III of New York City made a 4-foot putt on the 18th hole to edge England’s Gary Wolstenholme, 1-up, yesterday in the first round of match play in the United States Amateur Golf Championship in Daly City, Calif. Thirty-two winners advanced to two rounds of play today.
